@startuml SEQ_06_SUBMISSION
' ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
' Spec Kit — Fiction Book Writing Preset
' Section 6 of 6: Submission
' ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

skinparam backgroundColor #FAFAFA
skinparam sequenceArrowThickness 2
skinparam roundcorner 8
skinparam sequenceParticipantBorderColor #555555
skinparam sequenceParticipantBackgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam noteBorderColor #AAAAAA
skinparam noteBackgroundColor #FFFFF0

actor Author
participant "speckit.synopsis" as SYN #Honeydew
participant "speckit.query" as QR #Lavender
participant "speckit.export" as EX #Lavender
participant "speckit.audiobook" as AUD #PaleTurquoise

== Submission ==

Author -> SYN: draft (or update post-draft)
SYN --> Author: synopsis.md (one-page 250–350w + full 1,000–2,000w)

note right of SYN
  Both formats reveal the ending.
  Run after plan (outline) or
  after drafting (accuracy).
  Required before query letter.
end note

Author -> QR: draft
QR --> Author: query-letter.md (250–350 words)

Author -> QR: update / track / comp-titles
QR --> Author: submission tracker updated

Author -> EX: docx / epub / latex
EX --> Author: submission-ready manuscript file

opt Audiobook production
  Author -> AUD: voice add [narrator/character]
  AUD --> Author: constitution.md updated (## X. Audiobook Production)
  Author -> AUD: lexicon add [word]
  AUD --> Author: pronunciation entry registered
  Author -> AUD: lexicon export
  AUD --> Author: audiodraft/lexicon.pls (W3C PLS 1.0)
  Author -> AUD: draft all
  AUD --> Author: audiodraft/*.ssml + audiodraft/*_el.xml
  Author -> AUD: check
  AUD --> Author: stale / missing audiodraft report
  Author -> EX: audio
  EX --> Author: audiodraft/manifest.md (chapter manifest)
  note right of AUD
    TTS engines: Azure / Google /
    Amazon Polly (SSML) or ElevenLabs.
    Single or multi-speaker mode.
    Per-chapter files only — do not
    concatenate before ACX submission.
  end note
end

@enduml
